	This is a list of everyone that has helped in the development of ProjectileLib.
	
	- VolcanoINC		Original creator of the simulation, and the one maintaining and updating it.
	- DataSynchronized	Lots of testing, stress testing, bug fixing and the original particle effects.
	- VariadicFunction	Added bullet holes and made particles dynamically colored (feature taken from his own version)
	- einsteinK			The highly optimized internal projectile handler function
--]]]]></ProtectedString>
