							<Properties>
								<ProtectedString name="Source"><![CDATA[--[=[

innocent start

Wh... where am I...?
What is this place...
This is not what I remember...
Come on... wake up... wake up...
I got to get out of here...
Something’s wrong. I can feel it...
Don't worry... just stay calm.. you'll be okay.
I don't know where I am, I don't like this place...
I didn't wake up to this...
There's gotta be someone else here... right?
I need to find someone... anyone...
A place like this means structure... Structure means patterns...
I need to find a pattern... a way out...

vigi start

If I get questioned... I'm saying it was self defense.
I'm not gonna run. I'm gonna fight back.
Whatever this place is, I'm keeping this with me...
Im hearing commotion... I should be a hero...
I won't use this... unless I have to.
If I see something weird, I'm gonna use it...
I don't wanna use this... but I think I have to.
This is for my own safety...

killer start

I'm gonna find them... I can't die like this...
Anyone I see... they will be mine...
Everyone here is a target... I won't take chances...
I hear noises... They want me to use it... and I will.
Nobody can survive... nobody can...
I smell something... it's perfect...
It's about time I used this...
I'm gonna use it... and I'm gonna use it well...

killer dies to vigi
 
survivor

I heard something... does this mean I'm safe..?
There's no more threat... right?
I don't know what's going on... but... I think i'm safe...
...Whatever that was... I think it's gone now...
I think I'm safe now... I can rest...
I hope this means I'm safe... I don't wanna be here anymore...

vigilante

I did what I had to... right?
Well... I did what I had to do...
No more running... no more hiding.
I hope that was the right call...
I didn’t have a choice...
At least no one else has to die...
This weapon... I never wanted it.
At leat I don't have to use this again...
I don't know what I would have done without it...
Wow... Imagine what it would've been like if I didn't have this...

killer dies cuz they're too late lol idiot

survivor

I didn't see them... but I think we might just get out alive...
Okay... I think it's gone...
It's over... I think...
I heard something... but I don't know what it was...
I hope whatever I heard was the end...
Okay... no more hiding... I need to get out...
I hope that mean't I, or... anyone, didn't have to fight...

vigilante

I hope that meant I didn't have to use this...
...Maybe that's for the best
It better be over... I don't want anything on me...
Well... I was ready.. but I’m glad I didn’t have to...
I didn't have to use this... I'm glad...

killer kills everyone :O

killer

Good... I'm satisfied...
I could do this forever...
Finally... silence...
Nobody could run from me... Not even anyone...
I never knew it could be this easy...
It had to be done...
I'm glad I could do this...
That's better...
Peace... at last...
I don't have to worry anymore...

vigi hurts innocent

survivor

OW- WHAT THE?!
WAIT! What are you doing?!
ACK- WAIT!! STOP!!
PLEASE! I didn't do anything... I SWEAR!
HOLD ON! I'm not a threat... I promise!
WH- what are you doing?! I have nothing on me!!
DOES IT LOOK LIKE I HAVE ANYTHING ON ME?!
I JUST WANT TO GET OUT! PLEASE!
STOP!! I'M NOT A THREAT!! I SWEAR!!

vigilante

Wait- I’m sorry!
WAIT- I thought you were-!
Don't move, I won’t do it again!
HOLD ON! That was a mistake-
WAIT! I didn’t mean to-
I didn't mean to hurt you!

vigi kills innocent wow

vigilante

...
I can't believe I did that...
I feel like a murder now...
This wasn't what I intended to do...
No.. no no no...
What have I done...
I killed the wrong person...
I’m done... I’m done.
I can’t do this anymore...
This isn’t justice...
I’m just as bad...
I shouldn’t have had this...
I don’t deserve this...

innocent hurt by killer

survivor

OW- WHAT THE?!
AHHHHH!!!
WAIT! STOP!!
STOP!! PLEASE!!!
WAIT! PLEASE SPARE ME!!!
PLEASE- YOU DON'T HAVE TO DO THIS!!
NO!!! PLEASE!!!


killer kills innocent

killer

Not enough…
I need more...
One isn’t enough...
More... give me more...
They're all the same...
Keep running... I enjoy it.
You won’t be the last.
I’m not done yet...
Who’s next...?

]=]]]></ProtectedString>
